        <div id="HDNPluck_article_paratext" style="display: none;" class="entry-summary">[...] place your breadcrumbs (or other crumbs) into the third dish.

[...] press the meat into the crumbs, coating evenly.

In reality, searing or browning meat or fish creates a caramelized, golden crust that adds texture and a depth of flavor.

To brown, heat a completely dry pan, then add...</div>
